Another tip: Watch Slow TV!!

There are a bunch of good quality slow tv videos on YouTube. You can go on a train ride through the Swiss Mountains, a boat ride through the English Canals, or walk through the Streets of Japan!

Get a feel for the places you want to travel to and feel calmer at the same time.
